Get ready to turn up the volume and hit the dance floor! The ultimate party anthem you've been waiting for is finally here!

Gaanchill Music proudly presents "Moyna | ময়না," a musical masterpiece guaranteed to make every celebration unforgettable. This is the ultimate party song, wedding song, and dance song of the year!

Witness the magical chemistry between the incredible Bubly and Zibon as they bring energy to the screen. Let the powerful voices of Konal & Niloy mesmerize you, set to the poetic genius of Asif Iqbal's lyrics and an unforgettable, foot-tapping tune by the one and only Akassh Sen. Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..

Jaadu hi kar diya

Pardesiya..
